author: Vignesh Ganesan
text:
I‚Äôve been a regular at this gym for a while now, and I couldn‚Äôt be happier with my experience. The facilities are clean, well-maintained, and equipped with everything you need for a great workout. The overall atmosphere is friendly and motivating, which makes it a place I genuinely look forward to coming to.

A special mention to my personal trainer, Georgina‚Äîshe‚Äôs been absolutely fantastic! She takes the time to understand my goals, health needs, and fitness levels, and customizes each workout to suit me perfectly. Her encouragement, patience, and expertise keep me motivated throughout every session. Thanks to her guidance, I feel stronger, healthier, and more confident each day.

author: Min Toh
text:
I was quite apprehensive to join the gym initially as I'm a total newbie to fitness. But the decision to join and train with Georgina has been one of the best decisions that I've made for my health. Georgina is very patient and very knowledgeable. Under her guidance, I gained much progress in my fitness, health and confidence. She takes time to explain and teach me the correct forms and what to look out for and will adjust to my level. She is friendly, firm and encouraging. Due to her coaching, I was encouraged to keep strength training as part of my routine.
The gym is clean, well maintained and I always feel comfortable here. I also find the gym at SKH very well equipped compared to some other AF that I went to.

author: Adilah
text:
Had the privilege of training with Shahrul at AF SKH, and I‚Äôm beyond grateful for his guidance and motivation throughout my fitness journey. Thank you, Shahrul, for always pushing me (even when I complained üòÖ) and for sharing so much of your knowledge and experience. You‚Äôve taught me not just how to train better, but how to stay consistent, disciplined, and intentional.

It‚Äôs been such a rewarding journey, and I‚Äôve grown stronger both physically and mentally thanks to your patience and encouragement. Really couldn‚Äôt have asked for a better trainer to start this journey with. üí™üèº

author: Mark
text:
Been here for over a year. Honestly one of the better AF gyms in SG. Very well maintained, and the staff team care a lot about running the gym. Very responsive to enquiries and even decorates the gym with the festive seasons.

Downsides: Can get very crowded sometimes (Sengkang issue), and the aircon might be too weak for some, especially when there are a lot of people in the gym

author: Henri
text: This is by far the best Anytime Fitness I‚Äôve visited in Singapore. The facilities are fully equipped, cleanliness is consistently maintained, and most importantly, the staff are cheerful, warm, and welcoming. They go above and beyond to ensure members feel at home. It‚Äôs truly a fantastic community fostered by both the staff and fellow members.

author: dasun maduwantha
text: I‚Äôve had a great experience at Anytime Fitness. The gym is always kept very clean and well-maintained, which makes workouts much more enjoyable. The staff are friendly, professional, and always ready to help when needed. It‚Äôs a welcoming environment that makes you feel comfortable every time you visit.

author: Samara ‚ÄúMARA‚Äù M
text: First time visiting this branch and chased out for improper shoes??? It was covered leather slides. Never been an issue in other branches. Staff member did not even introduce herself and straight up told me to leave after I warmed up. Did not offer alternatives. What is the point of being so strict we are all adults? So ridiculous.

author: Pamela Lalu
text: I‚Äôve been training at this gym for a while now, and I couldn‚Äôt be happier with the experience. The environment is always welcoming, and the staff are incredibly friendly. Special shoutout to coach Valerie‚Äîsuper approachable, supportive, and genuinely passionate about helping me reach my fitness goals. Whether you‚Äôre a beginner or experienced, you‚Äôll definitely feel comfortable and motivated here. Highly recommend!

author: DD
text: Been coming to this gym for almost a year even though it‚Äôs not my main one, just for a change of environment sometimes. Staff and manager are really friendly which is great. Only thing is the music- it‚Äôs mostly old school songs and doesn‚Äôt really hype people up to train. Would be awesome if the playlist could be more upbeat. Thanks!

author: Helen CL
text:
I signed up for personal training at Anytime Fitness SKH to improve my overall health, and it has been a great experience. The staff are very friendly and helpful. I highly recommend my coach, Shahrul ‚Äî he is attentive, professional, and meticulous about correcting my posture in every detail.

He makes the most of our rest time by checking in on my nutrition and generously sharing his knowledge. Through our sessions, I‚Äôve not only gained physical strength but also developed a deeper understanding of how our body and muscles work.

Training with Coach Shahrul has been consistently pleasant and rewarding ‚Äî I always look forward to our sessions.

author: Nur Fadzillah
text: This gym is exceptionally clean, well-equipped, and has a motivating atmosphere that keeps me coming back. The staff are friendly, professional, and always ready to assist with any workout needs.

author: Addison Montgomery
text:
LONG OVERDUE REVIEW:

I had 1.5 yrs subscription, but seldom visited the gym because on the first day I was supposed to start, I asked the staff if he can show me around the gym as I wasn't familiar with the equipments - he said this is pretty much it and then a patron laughed at my face. Well it is funny, the place is quite small.
I am pretty self conscious already having to start going to the gym alone, that interaction pretty much ruined it for me. Wanna get a membership again but definitely not in this branch, it's small and doesn't even have classes!

author: Porky Goh
text: Gym is well maintained and staffs are helpful. The personal trainers are professional and gives insightful advise to help achieve your goals.

author: S. Soong
text: Staff here is friendly and environment is clean. Wish there‚Äôs a little more amenities like specific soaps and some facial cream for ladies.

author: T Maruthuvel
text: I have been coming for quite a while now. Great gym spacious and clean. Don't have much interaction with the staff but they seem to be friendly. They have been adding new stuff like the attachment rack. Would be 5 stars if they had some rarer equipments such as hack squat/pendulum squat/machine lateral raise.

author: Wilson Zhang
text:
If you‚Äôre looking to learn strength training safely, I can highly recommend reaching out to the trainers at SKHCampus. Having trained at this gym with Shahrul as my trainer for the last 9 months, I can attest to his high level of professionalism in tailoring and executing a program suitable to your workout objectives, commitment to client safety, and above all he possesses a positive attitude for those who appreciate a kind and warm trainer!

-

Having no real training in weightlifting and a several injuries, I was encouraged by a fellow gym member‚Äôs stellar review of Shahrul and sought his coaching to help gain muscles and joint stability.

Here‚Äôs some notable experiences in my journey thus far:

1. Looking to YouTube for exercise guidance does not make up for having an experienced trainer who can tailor exercises suitable for your needs and provide immediate feedback on joint positioning and simply if you‚Äôre doing the exercises effectively and safely. I now know with greater certainty after training with Shahrul what exercises to perform at the gym, and can confidently do them safely and that helps a lot in being consistent!

2. Nutrition is a key focus for building muscle mass. I was tracking macros prior to this but Shahrul goes above and beyond to tailor my  caloric plan and macros based on my needs as they evolve - from recomp, to bulking and now a cut. The gym also has in-house body scanner to estimate muscle and fat mass which is used for monthly check-in on progress.

3. ‚ÄúHomework‚Äù is assigned as beyond the two one hour sessions with Shahrul, he provides a list of exercises, set and rep ranges and additional guidance for self-training to hit all muscle groups sufficiently. This helped me understand what exercises to focus on consistently over the months and learn a routine for myself as I progress to self-training. Myself for instance I have to focus on training my lats, hamstrings and glutes more as they respond slower to stimulus.

4. Rest and recovery are also as important as that‚Äôs when muscles grow. Shahrul provided lots of great advice to help me get healthier beyond just the workouts in the gym.

I hope this helps if you have suffered from injuries and generally trying to achieve some fitness goals to reach out to Shahrul for a consultation. Cheers.

author: Zann Lee
text: Very well equipped gym even though it‚Äôs not very big, the staff here are all very friendly and welcoming too! Signed up with PT Georgina and it was one of the best decisions made :> she‚Äôs friendly and patient, always making sure that we‚Äôre pushing enough for each session and also making sure that we are doing the exercises in the right form :D i do wish the gym could be abit colder though

author: Angelicka Atendido
text: Has great equipment and the gym is always well-maintained and clean. The staff are always smiling and friendly, willing to help anytime. The space is decent, not too crowded but of course peak hours can be a bit tight but not so bad. Overall, I appreciate the convenience and the overall maintenance.

author: diyana Rahman
text: Pretty great gym! Good equipment and great staff and equipment. staff was friendly and encouraging. would definitely recommend others to sign up here too!!

author: _dapanda_
text: I‚Äôve been here for more than a year now, though not very active, I must say the staff here are the most amazing bunch! I had Gina as my PT for a while to learn how to use the equipment and pick up proper gym techniques. She‚Äôs incredibly patient, knowledgeable, and always so encouraging (she will keep adding the weights to maxxxxxx hahaha)‚Äî she really made a difference in my gym journey. Even when I‚Äôm not training with her, Gina still look out for me SHES DA BEST, and the team is always approachable and ready to help. It‚Äôs such a supportive and welcoming environment, and I‚Äôm glad to be a part of this gym!

author: QF
text: Been a member here at AFSKH for a couple of years now, nvr ceases to impress me. Staffs are extremely friendly, equipment are well maintained, cleanliness is top notched as well. Definitely one of the better AF gyms out there in SG!

author: Bubbly Banana
text:
Been going to this gym for about 6 months now. My first time entering this gym, I must've looked a little lost because the staff at the front desk asked if it was my first time here, and then proceeded to point out where the lockers were. That was nice.

When I was just starting out, multiple people here also voluntarily gave me tips on my form when they saw me performing the exercise wrongly, which I found really wholesome and appreciated. People here are also usually very willing to share equipment. Most people also wipe down the equipment after use. The equipment is well-maintained, no complaints whatsoever.

There is only one downside; it gets pretty crowded 4pm onwards, and sometimes even at 11pm its still pretty crowded. So I usually try to go late morning/early afternoon. Despite that, Anytime Fitness SKH still deserves 5 stars. I don't smile much, but just wanna let the staff know I appreciate this place. Keep up the good work.

author: Trevor Sze
text: I've been to all of the 120+ AF locations, and I like this one a lot, even though it is not one of those mega outlets with every single machine there is. The equipment is clean and the selection adequate, with ample enough space to not feel cramped. Free weights and stack weights are clearly defined, and showers are clean. Staff here are incredibly helpful and friendly, which really helps to add to a pleasant gym experience.

author: Adrian Lee
text:
2 years now at this gym. Most of the equipment here fits my routine. Staff and coaches are friendly too and always greets with a nice smileüòÅ

Afternoon is the best time to visit because there is not much crowd. If you are a late night gymmer usually it is still crowded around 10pm+

author: Matthew Song
text:
The facility and equipment are good. As a beginner, I definitely have no complaints. It can get a bit crowded during certain times, which given its size is expected. It's not small, but not big either. I'd say it's appropriate to serve the number of staff and community near by.

There are a few showers, the toilet outside is close enough to not be inconvenient and there's a decent amount of space to put your bags.

All the staff are extremely friendly and supportive, with special shoutout to my trainer Sharul. If not for him, I doubt I'd be where I am today.

author: Reach (Boybabyrage)
text: The gym is not big nor small. Good enough to do the work out with enough equipment. I like that it's not too crowded even during peak hours.

author: Asffaq Muhammad
text:
AF, never fails with well maintained equipment at most branches I‚Äôve been too

SKH Branch,  home club ‚Äî> kind & friendly peeps around you as you train

author: Pearline
text: Finally made the decision to sign up for gym 1 year ago. My Fun and Bubbly PT Gina have been there since day 1 guiding and teaching me the proper workout forms and personalising my workout to suit my needs and goals. She also helped me in strengthening my injured knees and since then, I am feeling more stronger and most importantly , it has improved my daily functionality and stamina that motivate me to continue to be more active.

text: This AF gym has 4 power racks and 1 smith machine. The equipment and machines are new, and the management is swift to repair or replace any broken or old equipment. Most of the time, it is crowded and does not have much space for free weight. Overall, it's still 1 of the best AF gym.

author: Tinie Ng
text: Staff was very helping in teaching how to use the gym equipments. Clean facility!

author: Jensen Tan
text:
first time ever entering into a gym and needed a personal trainer. I was very fortunate to have personal trainer Shahrul to guide me in my 24-session journey. He's very patient, friendly, and makes me comfortable and at ease every time I train with him.

It was a fruitful self-discovery journey with him also, where beyond just trying to bulk up, I gained useful knowledge on my diet, the value of building strength into old age, having a mental space to relax during workouts, and building good health habits. It definitely has given me positive impact to my overall well-being.

I would recommend anyone to go with a personal trainer (esp newbies) as it helps to ensure that you can develop good postures, avoid injuries, and a source of motivation. Shahrul is a great help in Sengkang area so I highly recommend him!

author: V Kappiyan
text: The gym has a lot of good equipment and facilities. I personally have benefited a lot from the personal coaching and have improved on my fitness. Coach Shahrul has guided me and motivated throughout all the session which helped me to give my fullest effort.

author: Goi Rui An Andy (Skss)
text: AF SKH is the best gym I have went to, been about a year since I signed up. The gym feels inclusive as the members and staff there are extremely welcoming. I also like that there are challenges every few months for members to participate and to have fun in to win the attractive prizes. text: Love SKGH AF! It‚Äôs my home gym. Equipment here is all good, super clean space too! Shahmi is the friendliest staff here, radiating positive vibes! Solid one la

text:

All staff are friendly. The gym is clean, the equipment is well maintained. Normally the morning and afternoon time the gym is not so busy.

author: Kymberly Tan
text:
The staff at AF SKH are consistently friendly and welcoming, creating a positive atmosphere from the moment you walk in. The equipment is well-maintained and clean, ensuring a comfortable and safe environment for your workout.

A special mention for my PT, Georgina. Her focus on proper form ensures clients train safely and target the intended muscle groups effectively, leading to improved strength. Georgina incorporates a variety of exercises into our sessions, keeping them dynamic, engaging, and challenging. Beyond her expertise, her approachable personality fosters an enjoyable training experience for clients.

Overall, I highly recommend AF SKH to anyone seeking a well-equipped, clean gym with friendly and supportive staff.

author: He dreamh8
text: Crowd is ok and I always manage to use the facility as planned. Staff are friendly and helpful. Been using personal trainer more than one year. Trainer Shahrul is very professional and trustworthy.

author: Kyla Johari
text: Ahhh where do i start? AFSKH is truly one of of the best gyms I‚Äôve ever visited! All the trainers, and the gym manager (shoutout to you Ali) are very kind and helpful and they always make me feel welcomed whenever i come to the gym. The gym is well equipped and always kept clean which I appreciate alot. No other gym will ever have my heart like AFSKH ‚ù§Ô∏è

text: Just went to inquire at this gym. Staff member there was extremely rude. I It‚Äôs obvious from the get go that I wasn‚Äôt the type of person she would welcome to her gym. author: Muhammad Akashah

author: Elhan

author: Siyi

author: Tiff
text: Friendly trainers, clean environment. Place is accessible. If you want a more friendly environment to gym, here‚Äôs the place!

text: Friendly staff and great facility, responds quickly and promptly to inquiries and questions. VERY FRIENDLY AND APPROACHABLE PEEPS!

author: Yi Ran
text:
I've been a regular customer here for a year. Everything else is good, except for one major issue.

More than half of all the 10kg weights here are off-scale. Some are lighter and heavier, and it really disrupts my workout, potentially increasing the risk of injury, in my opinion.

This has been a long-term issue, and many of my friends I met here at this gym have also raised the issue with management before. Nothing has been done since last year...

text: The gym is clean and well equipped. I found it odd the gym does not provide any yoga mats to perform stretching though they do have these in premises. When asked I was told to stretch on the floor which I refused politely as members walk over with their shoes and I didn‚Äôt not feel comfortable laying my head on a floor which is very communal.

author: Nurul Shehan
text: Gym equipment is good. Staff is friendly. Will visit again

author: Raeis Azrin
text: Cozy gym with most of the equipments one may need. Exceptional staff, especially Shahmi because he went above and beyond to help many of the gym goers

author: Demas Ong
text:
Anytime Fitness is a fantastic gym with a welcoming and supportive community, and their staff are a huge part of what makes it such a great place to work out.

The staff at Anytime Fitness are knowledgeable, friendly, and always willing to lend a hand! Shout out to all of them!

author: Kathleen Salazar
text: Good gym with good equipment but really too many people. Always need to wait. Even at 11pm at night. Very frustrating. But not the gyms fault nor the people. AF please open one more in Sengkang or at least buy over the Sakae Sushi area. Cannot tahan.

author: Nor Syahid
text:
A fairly good gym.
But the users seems to lack etiquette.
Weights are always being left on the floor, they do not re rack after using and even if they do, it'll always be disorderly.
20s mixed with 10s, 5s and so on.
I have seen users working out in flip flops and crocs and even once i saw a dude in his full office attire.
Dress shoes and all.
Gym staff do not enforce etiquettes enough.

author: ahNah
text: Manager, trainer and staff are very friendly, Trainer Georgina is very patient and details, guide me well to train my weak area and challenge me from time to time. Nice !

author: Anzer Tan
text: Forced to pay an extra month at the gym although i had already stated my interest in cancelling early. Staff said will help to cancel but did not mention the need to send an email prior to the end of the membership. How can the staff forget about such an important detail regarding payment? The staff should adopt a more proactive attitude in serving their customers better. I hope other customers are reminded to send a email to confirm their membership cancellation. üò§

author: Paul Young
text:
This gym is a very nice place to workout.
The staff is very friendly and always ready to help, the music choice is very modern and upbeat, the place is clean, and everyone is happy to take turns, share equipment etc.

A great environment for one to become the best version of themselves.

author: K P
text: As an amateur gym-goer, I never felt intimidated here, thanks to the welcoming staff and community. Cozy but well-maintained gym. Always a joy to workout here.

author: Priscilla Lin
text:
I've been going to Anytime Fitness for over half a year now. The staff here are all very friendly, the environment is clean, and the gym equipment is well-maintained.

I want to give a special thanks to my personal trainer, Shahrul. He's been coaching me for over 4 months, and he's a very dedicated and responsible trainer. Every time we have a session, his positive energy uplifts me. He's also very patient and continuously encourages me to push my limits when I doubt myself. Whenever I exercise, he always focuses on watching each of my movements carefully to ensure they are correct, correcting my posture to prevent injury.

After our sessions, he plans out a workout schedule for me to follow, including specific weights and sets. Even when he's not around, I have a structured training plan to follow, so I know exactly what exercises to do without wasting time at the gym. I remember during my last InBody measurement, the results were not as expected. Although I usually exercise diligently, I haven't been controlling my diet properly, and I also dislike doing aerobic exercise. I can feel that he is even sadder than I am because he once told me that seeing his students make progress bit by bit gives him a great sense of achievement and happiness. After that day, I set clear goals for myself. I explicitly told him what I wanted, and he actively helped me plan my daily calorie intake and advised me on my daily nutritional needs. With his provided training regimen, I diligently followed through. In just three weeks, I successfully reduced over 3% body fat and gained 1 kg of muscle. Initially, I doubted my abilities, but because of his dedication and encouragement, I was inspired to strive for my goals.

I also admire his passion for every student. Regardless of how early or late it is, he accommodates his students' schedules. Whether during class or privately, he's always enthusiastic to answer any questions and find solutions to my problems.

If you're looking to start your fitness journey but don't know where to begin, I sincerely recommend finding Shahrul. He won't be harsh on you, but he'll listen to your needs seriously. He customizes workouts based on each person's weaknesses, helping you fall in love with fitness and become better!

I'm truly grateful to have met such an amazing coach because he has helped me become better and better! His guidance has been instrumental in my fitness journey, and I'm immensely grateful for his support.

author: Ayesha Lee
text: Great staff. Our personal trainer, Gina is amazing. Friendly, professional, and accomodating. Provided customized programs. Highly recommend!

author: James Goh
text:
SKH AF Campus is an amazing gym
with great amenities! The staffs are very warm towards their members, smiling and greeting member whenever they enter. They are often on the lookout for safety and cleanliness.
Great vibe, great staffs!

author: Mohamed khalid Mishal
text: The trainers and Staff at Anytime fitness SKG campus are always supportive and have good friendships with the client. They will always check up on you after every training session and go out of the way to help you too.Coach Shahrul was always helpful and supporive..he went out of his way many times to ensure the client's wellbeing...very kind,responsible and competent coach üëçüèΩ 10/10 experience‚ò∫Ô∏è

author: Twain Teo
text: Fantastic gym, recently upgraded with new equipment. Kept very clean, staff is friendly and general crowd is a good mix of veteren trainees to beginners. Welcoming environment though it can get a bit crowded during peak hours as most gyms tend to.

author: QZ Goh
text:
Started off going to the gym without any experience but gained lots of it after a few months of training with Gina. She has shown me how to achieve my fitness goal and has also shared countless tips and tricks to help me make healthier choices outside of the gym. She truly cares about my progress, and it shows in the time and effort she puts into her work. She is always available to answer questions or offer advice, even outside of our regular training sessions. Do look for her if you need a personal trainer; she will gladly assist you with your goals.

Keep Flexing!

author: Skylar Chng
text: Signed up for my son at another outlet. He had been to a few outlets near Sengkang before but I must say SKH AF has the best customer service so far. All the staffs there are super friendly and helpful and most importantly they listen to our needs and it definitely makes us feel at ease. Thumbs up to Ali, the outlet manager and his team. Keep up the good work üí™üí™

author: Venkatesh Visvanathan
text: When I first joined Anytime Fitness, it had been 20 years since I had last exercised at the gym. I remember feeling hesitant and anxious about restarting my fitness journey, given my age and lack of experience. However, my personal trainer, Sharul, helped me regain my confidence and realise that age is just a number when it comes to fitness. Every session, he would give his 200% to guide me through various exercises while ensuring I was doing alright and able to cope with the intensity of the exercises. He would encourage me to push myself but at the same time show me how I can modify exercises to gradually build up my strength. Sharul is knowledgeable, friendly, accomodating, dedicated and very committed and I would highly recommend him to anyone looking to embark on their fitness journey. Under his training, I am sure they too will be able to gain confidence in themselves, and become motivated to put in consistent effort to see growth in small steps, just like how I did!

author: XI EN TOH
text: sign up around may of 2022. the environment is great. the staff was super nice. especially Shahmi, he was very patient he answered all my questions take me around on my first day. help me out with some gym tips also! diligent staff, love doing his job!  hope he gets a well deserved pay increase!

author: richard tan
text: this outlet equipment well maintain. outlet manager make it a point to help and greet every member. This service level should be emulated across all AF outlets

author: Mik Mohsen
text: Very good experience, staff were very helpful :)

author: Shahrin Shukor
text: Friendly staff who are happy to assist anytime. Premises are clean and even have showers. Equipment are well maintained and easy to use with not too many people even during peak periods. Excellent value proposition for myself!

author: Ahmad Khairul
text:
Great staff running the gym. Very friendly and motivating. Good vibes all the time. Gym abit crowded at times but if i want an empty gym, must pay more and go  private boutique gym which is not even 24 hrsü§£

author: Tay Bernard
text: Had a great experience with Georgina. she's a wonderful trainer who pushes you towards your fitness goals. Highly recommend her

author: K O
text: Visited as an Australian AF member. In terms of the size, I was deceived by the pictures (cue the laughter)! But I have to say, this was a very clean and well-maintained gym. The constraints of space made the walkways rather narrow (hard to social distance). Muhammad (the gym manager) was very hospitable and welcoming. No wide cable machine to use though (possibly cos of the small space). Disposable sanisiting wipes provided so members could help with keeping the gym clean and sanitary. Would recommend coming here if you are doing some ‚Äúmaintenance‚Äù work while on your trip to Singapore.

author: Ashiq Ali
text:
I engaged Shahrul as my personal trainer for 12 weeks to recover my mobility in my right arm as i had under gone a shoulder surgery.

Shahrul is knowledgeable in sports injury recovery and has passion to aid anyone who is in need. He goes above and beyond to answer all my queries which i had asked him over the 12 weeks.
His approach to fitness is focusing on the basics and getting it right and that alone will produce significant results and it work me.

I managed to gain considerable amount of mobility and strength on my injured arm and gain over muscle mass in this 12 weeks.For those who are looking for someone to help with your recovery due to an injury or strengthening your current mobility you may engage him.

I will be going back to him in the future when im on  my next phase of training.

Shahrul your passion for fitness and sport recovery is commendable and keep up with the passion and enthusiasm that you posses.

author: God's Amazing Grace
text:
I would like to take the opportunity in this review to say a big thank you to Mr Omar , fitness member who trained at your gym .

Mr Omar is a GOD sent passer-by who readily assisted me at the entrance of sengkang hospital on April 24 2022 (Sunday night).

He kindly got me a wheelchair and walked me to the a & e and stayed on till registration is done.
Despite the fact that he was already late for his physical training at the gym.

I am so thankful to you Mr Omar and I know you will make a wonderful occupational therapist.
Wishing you all the very best for your endeavour.

GOD bless you.
